{"id":231875924,"title":"膦酸鹽vs磷酸鹽","content":"小弟偶爾會逛賣場來增加愛用產品名單\n逛全聯時看到德國P牌和D牌洗精，但看到後面寫著膦酸鹽\nhttps://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkF.jpg\n德國福斯造假數據後對德國的東西稍微扣了點分\n雖說磷酸鹽這種成份禁很久了，但大廠留著非法物質也不是沒案例。可口可樂也被爆出在亞洲版的飲料中繼續加焦糖色素這種致癌物（美國版的早就移除了）\n\n有人對膦酸鹽vs磷酸鹽比較有研究的嗎？\n不想讓自己在不知不覺間破壞生態環境","excerpt":"小弟偶爾會逛賣場來增加愛用產品名單，逛全聯時看到德國P牌和D牌洗精，但看到後面寫著膦酸鹽，德國福斯造假數據後對德國的東西稍微扣了點分，雖說磷酸鹽這種成份禁很久了，但大廠留著非法物質也不是沒案例。可口可","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-17T02:06:44.751Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-17T02:06:44.751Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["環保","愛地球","污染","磷酸鹽"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"培根沙拉蛋","department":"insanelyomelet","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkF.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"0e59050f-1b7a-43a5-a126-3b2ebb13ca10","url":"https://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkFl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkFl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkFl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-17T02:06:44.751Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-17T02:06:44.751Z"},{"id":"0e59050f-1b7a-43a5-a126-3b2ebb13ca10","url":"https://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkF.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/SdQ7MkF","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/SdQ7MkFl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-17T02:06:44.751Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-17T02:06:44.751Z"}],"postAvatar":""}